<template>
    <input type="text" v-model="textField" />
    <button>확인</button>
</template>
<script setup>
    import { ref, defineProps } from 'vue'

    const props = defineProps({
        value : {
            type : String,
            default : ()=>{
                return "";
            }
        }
    })
    const textField = ref(props.value)
    console.log("props.value : ",props.value)
    console.log("textField : ",textField)
</script>
